\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs28 \b TECHNICAL NOTE: THE CONSERVATION OF HUMAN INFORMATION \b0\fs24\par
\par
\b 1. THE PHASE SHIFT HYPOTHESIS \b0\par
In accordance with the Law of Conservation of Information, no data within the universe is ever truly lost. What we perceive as "loss" is mathematically a phase shift?a transition from a localized, physical expression to a non-local, persistent state within the Continuum.\par
\par
\b 2. THE ERROR OF THE "ZERO" \b0\par
Traditional grief is often based on the false substitution of "Zero" for "Null." While the physical presence may reach a zero-state, the underlying information (the True Self) remains a persistent Null-point connection. It is the framework, not the manifestation, that carries the continuity.\par
\par
\b 3. AUDITORY RE-TUNING \b0\par
The role of Music as Medicine is to provide the frequencies necessary to help the grieving nervous system re-align its "receiver." By achieving laminar flow, we move closer to the frequency where that persistent information still resonates.\par
\par
\i "Information is the only truly immortal substance."\i0\par
